TO USE 'APPLE.OUT'; BLOAD IT; THENTYPE 'PR#1' TO START PRINTER OUTPUT;THEN    'CALL 768'.AT THAT POINT; OUTPUT SHOULD BEDIRECTEDTO THE SCREEN UNLESS THEOPEN-APPLE KEY IS HELD DOWN; ANDTHEN IT GOES TO THE   PRINTER.  TRYIT BY LISTING A LARGE     PROGRAMAND ALTERNATELY HOLDING ANDRELEASING THE OPEN-APPLE KEY AS ITLISTS.